summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of Fifty six and 52/100 dollars ($56.52), or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, to pay the City's general taxes on a part of Lot "G", Block 16, Plat of Columbia; Lot 24, Interurban Addition; Lots 21 and 22, Block 5, Lake Dell Addition, and a part of Gov'mt. Lot 2, Section 13, Township 24 North, Range 3 East.
